"WAPT, Users, Package Deployer; Package Developer, SuperAdmin, Local "
"Administrator, availability, integrity, confidentiality, authenticity, "
"cyberdefense, ANSSI, security, cybersecurity"
msgstr ""
"WAPT, Utilisateur, Gestionnaire de Déploiement, Développeur de Paquets, "
