#: ../../source/wapt-security-principles/safety-principle.rst:530
msgid ""
"Security function F2: protecting the integrity of the installation "
"process of WAPT packages"
msgstr ""
"Fonction de sécurité F2 : Protection de l'intégrité du processus "
"d'installation des paquets WAPT"

#: ../../source/wapt-security-principles/safety-principle.rst:533
msgid "Security function F2A: signature of WAPT packages"
msgstr "Fonction de sécurité F2A : Signature des paquets WAPT"

#: ../../source/wapt-security-principles/safety-principle.rst:539
msgid ""
"to avoid an unauthorized entity modifying the content or the behavior of "
"a WAPT package;"
msgstr ""
"éviter qu'une entité non-autorisée modifie le contenu ou le comportement "
"d'un paquet WAPT ;"

#: ../../source/wapt-security-principles/safety-principle.rst:545
msgid ""
"when an :term:`Administrator` or a :term:`Package Deployer` builds a WAPT"
" package, the file :file:`manifest.sha256` is created that lists the "
"control sums of all files in the package;"
msgstr ""
"quand un :term:`Administrateur` ou un :term:`Déployeur de Paquets` "
"construit un paquet WAPT, un fichier :file:`WAPT\\manifest.sha256` est "
"créé qui liste les sommes de contrôle de tous les fichiers du paquet ;"

#: ../../source/wapt-security-principles/safety-principle.rst:549
msgid ""
"a file :file:`signature.sha256` **encrypted** with the WAPT agent's "
"private key is then created in the folder :file:`<WAPT>`; it contains the"
" control sum of the file :file:`manifest.sha256`;"
msgstr ""
"un fichier :file:`signature.sha256` **chiffré** avec la clé privée est "
"ensuite créé dans le dossier :file:`WAPT`, il contient la somme de "
"contrôle du fichier :file:`WAPT\\manifest.sha256` ;"

#: ../../source/wapt-security-principles/safety-principle.rst:553
msgid "the whole is then compressed and suffixed with a *.wapt* extension;"
msgstr "l'ensemble est archivé avec l'extension *.wapt* ;"

#: ../../source/wapt-security-principles/safety-principle.rst:555
msgid ""
"when a WAPT agent downloads a WAPT package, the agent checks that the "
"file :file:`signature.sha256` has been signed with the private key that "
"matches the certificate present in the folder :file:`certificate.crt`;"
msgstr ""
"quand un agent WAPT télécharge un paquet WAPT, l'agent vérifie que le "
"fichier :file:`signature.sha256` a été signé avec la clé privée qui "
"correspond au certificat présent dans le dossier "
":file:`WAPT\\certificate.crt` ;"

#: ../../source/wapt-security-principles/safety-principle.rst:559

msgid ""
"the WAPT agent then checks that the certificate or the chain of "
"certificates in :file:`certificate.crt` has been signed with a key "
"matching one of the certificates present in the folder "
":file:`C:\\\\Program Files (x86)\\\\wapt\\\\ssl`;"
msgstr ""
"l'agent WAPT vérifie ensuite que le certificat (ou la chaîne de "
"certificat) :file:`certificate.crt` a bien été signé avec une clé privée "
"correspondant à un des certificats présents dans le dossier "
":file:`C:\\Program Files (x86)\\wapt\\\\ssl` ;"

#: ../../source/wapt-security-principles/safety-principle.rst:564
msgid ""
"the WAPT agent then generates the control sum of all the files contained "
"in the package (except the files :file:`signature.sha256` and "
":file:`certificate.crt `) and verifies that it matches the file "
":file:`manifest.sha256` contained in the package;"
msgstr ""
"l'agent WAPT fait ensuite la somme de contrôle de tous les fichiers du "
"paquet (excepté les fichiers :file:`signature.sha256` et "
":file:`certificate.crt` ) et vérifie que cela correspond au fichier "
":file:`WAPT\\manifest.sha256` du paquet ;"

#: ../../source/wapt-security-principles/safety-principle.rst:569
msgid ""
"if one of these steps does not pass, this means that a file has been "
"modified/ added/ removed. The execution of the :file:`setup.py` is then "
"canceled."
msgstr ""
"si l'une de ces étapes n'est pas validée, alors cela signifie qu'un "
"fichier a été modifié / ajouté / supprimé. Alors, l'exécution du "
":program:`setup.py` est annulée ;"

#: ../../source/wapt-security-principles/safety-principle.rst:572
msgid ""
"the altered package is then deleted from the local cache and the event is"
" journalized in the logs of the agent;"
msgstr ""
"le paquet en défaut est ensuite supprimé du cache local ; l'évènement est"
" rapporté dans les log de l'agent ;"

#: ../../source/wapt-security-principles/safety-principle.rst:577
msgid ""
"Since the version 1.5 of WAPT, the format of the :file:`manifest` file "
"has changed from *sha1* to *sha256*."
msgstr ""
"Depuis la version 1.5, le fichier :file:`manifest` est passée de *sha1* à"
" *sha256*."

#: ../../source/wapt-security-principles/safety-principle.rst:581
