#: ../../source/wapt-security-principles/safety-principle.rst:589
msgid ""
"an unauthorized entity modifying WAPT dependencies on WAPT equipped "
"devices by falsifying :file:`https://waptserver/wapt/Packages`;"
msgstr ""
"éviter qu'une entité non-autorisée modifie des dépendances WAPT sur la "
"machine en falsifiant le fichier "
":file:`https://waptserver/wapt/Packages` ;"

#: ../../source/wapt-security-principles/safety-principle.rst:595
msgid ""
"When a WAPT package is signed, the sensitive attributes of the package "
"are listed inside the **signed_attributes** attribute of the control "
"file."
msgstr ""
"Lors de la signature d'un paquet WAPT, les attributs sensibles du paquet "
"sont listés dans l'attribut **signed_attributes**."

#: ../../source/wapt-security-principles/safety-principle.rst:600
msgid "Example of a *signed_attributes* list:"
msgstr "Exemple d'une liste *signed_attributes* :"

#: ../../source/wapt-security-principles/safety-principle.rst:602
msgid ""
"*package*, *version*, *architecture*, *section*, *priority*, "
"*maintainer*, *description*, *depends*, *conflicts*, *maturity*, "
"*locale*, *min_os_version*, *max_os_version*, *min_wapt_version*, "
"*sources*, *installed_size*, *signer*, *signer_fingerprint*, "
"*signature_date*, *signed_attributes*,"
msgstr ""
"*package*, *version*, *architecture*, *section*, *priority*, "
"*maintainer*, *description*, *depends*, *conflicts*, *maturity*, "
"*locale*, *min_os_version*, *max_os_version*, *min_wapt_version*, "
