msgstr ""
"éviter qu'une entité non-autorisée modifie le comportement de l'agent "
"WAPT ;"

#: ../../source/wapt-security-principles/safety-principle.rst:642

msgid ""
"The installation folder :file:`C:\\\\Program Files (x86)\\\\wapt` is "
